DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T2.value currency, T1.CapFloorVolatility, T1.id FROM ORE.dbo.TodaysMarketCapFloorVolatilities T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesCurrencyCode T2 ON T1.currency = T2.value

field.name: *currency
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value currency, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesCurrencyCode !T! ORDER BY value
